PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773363777
OL,3,CNeed for close Anglo-Irish ties has
OL,4,Cnever been greater, Martin tells
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FAt last year's summit, Mr Martin and
OL,8,FSir Keir committed themselves to a
OL,9,Fprogramme of co-operation between the
OL,10,Ftwo countries, called UK-Ireland 2030.
OL,12,FDelivering an address at a cultural
OL,13,Fevent, the Taoiseach said there was a
OL,14,F"renewed spirit of co-operation"
OL,15,Fbetween Ireland and the UK.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773363777
OL,3,CNeed for close Anglo-Irish ties has
OL,4,Cnever been greater, Martin tells
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FHe said: "As we look to 2030, our task
OL,8,Fis clear ` to deepen co-operation in
OL,9,Fthe areas that matter most to our
OL,10,Fcitizens, such as infrastructure
OL,11,Fdelivery, especially housing; clean
OL,12,Fenergy, climate action, research and
OL,13,Finnovation, the cost of living;
OL,14,Freadying our economies and our workers
OL,15,Ffor the industries of the future,
OL,16,Fprotecting our critical
OL,17,Finfrastructure, including under our
OL,18,Fseas.
OL,26,@oD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773363777
OL,3,CNeed for close Anglo-Irish ties has
OL,4,Cnever been greater, Martin tells
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,F"In all of this, crucially, we are
OL,8,Fworking together from a sense of
OL,9,Fshared values, whether that is in
OL,10,Finternational co-operation, in
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland, or in shaping a
OL,12,Ffairer, more prosperous future for all
OL,13,Facross these islands.
OL,15,F"As we gather, we are conscious also
OL,16,Fthat this is a changing, more
OL,17,Funcertain, and more unsettled world.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773363777
OL,3,CNeed for close Anglo-Irish ties has
OL,4,Cnever been greater, Martin tells
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,F"In that context, the case for an
OL,8,Factive, engaged and close partnership
OL,9,Fbetween our two countries has never
OL,10,Fbeen greater."
OL,12,FThe Prime Minister told the event that
OL,13,Fwe are in an age of "dramatic
OL,14,Funcertainty".
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@NO]uD@UOUvD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
