OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773363777
OL,3,CNeed for close Anglo-Irish ties has
OL,4,Cnever been greater, Martin tells
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FHe said: "The last just two weeks are
OL,8,Fa reminder of that uncertainty and I
OL,9,Fgenuinely believe that co-operation in
OL,10,Fperiods like this is more important
OL,11,Fnow than it's ever been to ensure that
OL,12,Fwe can deliver the security and the
OL,13,Fgrowth for our people, and to tackle
OL,14,Fthe thing that I know is in people's
OL,15,Fminds, which is the cost of living."
OL,17,FEarlier, Sir Keir and Mr Martin met
OL,18,Fbusiness leaders.
OL,26,@oD@JOUwD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
