OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773363777
OL,3,CNeed for close Anglo-Irish ties has
OL,4,Cnever been greater, Martin tells
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FEarlier, the British Prime Minister
OL,8,Fand Northern Ireland Secretary Hilary
OL,9,FBenn landed on the tarmac at Cork
OL,10,FAirport on Thursday evening after
OL,11,Fmeeting with Stormont's political
OL,12,Fleaders in Belfast earlier on Thursday.
OL,14,FThey were greeted by Mr Martin, the
OL,15,FBritish ambassador in Dublin Kara
OL,16,FOwen, and the Irish ambassador in
OL,17,FLondon Martin Fraser.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
