CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773363777
OL,3,CNeed for close Anglo-Irish ties has
OL,4,Cnever been greater, Martin tells
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FSeveral engagements are planned on
OL,8,FThursday and Friday as part of the UK-
OL,9,FIreland Summit, which was established
OL,10,Fto maintain and develop relations post-
OL,11,FBrexit.
OL,13,FFive million euros worth of cultural
OL,14,Fcollaborations for 12 projects, one of
OL,15,Fwhich involves a play starring Paul
OL,16,FMescal, were announced on Thursday to
OL,17,Fcoincide with the summit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
