PN,30212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773363777
OL,3,CNeed for close Anglo-Irish ties has
OL,4,Cnever been greater, Martin tells
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FHe added: "Our job is to manage
OL,8,Fthrough those issues and come to a
OL,9,Fproper resolution, rather than to
OL,10,Fescalate them.
OL,12,F"That's the basis on which I've
OL,13,Fworked, that's why the UK-Ireland
OL,14,Frelationship is in a better place and
OL,15,FI'll continue in that vein."
OL,26,@oD@KOUtD@AOUwD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
