OL,3,CNeed for close Anglo-Irish ties has
OL,4,Cnever been greater, Martin tells
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FAt the inaugural UK-Ireland Summit in
OL,8,FLiverpool last year, the leaders
OL,9,Flaunched a programme of co-operation
OL,10,Ffor the period up until 2030 `
OL,11,Fcovering trade, energy, maritime
OL,12,Fsecurity, emergency planning and
OL,13,Fcultural connections.
OL,15,FAt the Cork summit, Mr Martin and Sir
OL,16,FKeir are to focus on greater co-
OL,17,Foperation across areas such as
OL,18,Finfrastructure, clean energy, skills
OL,19,Fand innovation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
