PN,30214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773363777
OL,3,CNeed for close Anglo-Irish ties has
OL,4,Cnever been greater, Martin tells
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FThe two leaders are to take part in
OL,8,Fevents along the theme of Shared
OL,9,FProsperity, Shared Seas, Shared Ties,
OL,10,Fincluding a research-focused visit, a
OL,11,Fcultural reception and a discussion
OL,12,Fwith young people.
OL,14,FFive million euros worth of funding
OL,15,Fwas announced on Thursday for 12 joint
OL,16,FIreland-UK cultural projects between
OL,17,Fnow and 2030.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
