OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773363777
OL,3,CNeed for close Anglo-Irish ties has
OL,4,Cnever been greater, Martin tells
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FOne is a co-production between the
OL,8,FAbbey Theatre in Dublin and the
OL,9,FNational Theatre in London, starring
OL,10,Faward-winning actor Mescal in the play
OL,11,FA Whistle In The Dark.
OL,13,FOthers involve an "All-In" scheme to
OL,14,Fmake cultural spaces more accessible
OL,15,Ffor people with disabilities; a joint
OL,16,Fproject on the national archives of
OL,17,Fboth jurisdictions; and a joint
OL,18,Fresearch project between the National
OL,19,FMuseum of Ireland, the National Museum
OL,20,Fof Scotland and National Museums
OL,21,FLiverpool.
